cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.MM 

The paper focuses on cross-modal retrieval using deep neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also discusses the transfer of knowledge from single-modal datasets, which is related to transfer learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper evaluates its proposed method on three datasets, which is related to multimedia (cs.MM).
